- **`C:\Users\johnm\modular apartment planner\src\annotations\tags.js`** - Reference pattern: `applyCollisionOffsets` at line 122 is the proven template to follow
- **`C:\Users\johnm\modular apartment planner\src\renderers\TrussDetailRenderer.jsx`** - Verify compatibility: confirm no renderer changes needed since it already merges all tag arrays into `BlueprintAnnotationLayer`
- **`C:\Users\johnm\modular apartment planner\src\renderers\BlueprintAnnotationLayer.jsx`** - Verify leader line rendering: confirm `TagFigure` correctly renders shifted leader lines (it does -- it reads `tag.leaderLine.start` and `tag.leaderLine.end` directly)
